{"tid":2108001,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[又亮劍］反擊美對台售$48億武器 中國制裁美國軍火巨擘洛歇馬丁","createTime":"2020-07-14T08:51:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-14T12:45:39.000Z","uid":239336,"like":163,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":86,"replies":[{"pid":"4fc29671b28b571a80dedc8b87580385f51d0976","tid":2108001,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T08:51:01.000Z","msg":"中國針對美國國務院批准對台軍售，制裁美國軍火業巨擘洛歇馬丁（Lockheed Martin）。<br />\n<br />\n中國外交部發言人趙立堅周二（14日）在例行記者會上宣佈有關消息，他指，中方堅決反對美國對台軍售，敦促美方切實恪守一個中國原則和中美三個聯合公報規定，停止售台武器，以免進一步損害中美關係和台海和平穩定。<br />\n美國務院批准一項6.2億美元對台軍售案，國台辦發言人朱鳳蓮今日回應，堅決反對美國向台灣出售武器，反對台美進行任何形式的軍事聯繫。她說：「民進黨當局『以武謀獨』不會得逞，只會破壞台海和平穩定，給台灣人民帶來更大災難。」<br />\n美國兩家對台售武的公司雷神公司（Raytheon）和洛克希德馬丁公司，均位列世界五大國防和約商榜單。雖然中國實施制裁，但不少觀點認為鑑於美國軍火公司對華業務並不多，中國宣稱制裁最多只能起到震懾作用。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200714/3YAJQ4PEDD2IRO6OW6GCDFAY2I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200714%2F3YAJQ4PEDD2IRO6OW6GCDFAY2I%2F&d=fc%2FsVbAXSk%2FqMRyYewxCuK3e3GGuF%2FCnRpDBLK0zENU%3D&h=e9962a25\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200714%2F3YAJQ4PEDD2IRO6OW6GCDFAY2I%2F&h=9f207cdc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200714/3YAJQ4PEDD2IRO6OW6GCDFAY2I/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0yFdYx4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0yFdYx4.jpg&h=f3a7e062&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y71kDx5.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy71kDx5.gif&h=ef2162fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5qAET6t.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5qAET6t.gif&h=bd6cf47a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0f941f78e7ed470feeda454123674cd3e59364c0","tid":2108001,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T08:52:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"59e0